:bold;\">此间的少年x</span> 说: 很棒，我就想看这个，提个小建议，每年平均分能改成按季划分吗</q></div>接下来会做，不过不光是按季，最终目标是作品和用户的评分都至少可以细分到按月（对动画来说按季划分更有意义，但游戏来说可能用户更想看到发售当月的评分和接下来的评分变化）...这样应该可以满足大部分需求，但是有一个问题是图表的横向空间是有限的，如果一个08年的用户选择按月细分整张图可能因为数据点过多导致基本不可读，目前还正在思考怎么尽量清晰的展示数据点过多的图"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/00/74/7461.jpg","floor":"#17","id":"1384453","time":"2018-9-26 15:02","userId":"xorms","userName":"xorms","userSign":"","message":"不知道为什么，动画效果总是感觉慢个半拍","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/icon.jpg","floor":"#18","id":"1384455","time":"2018-9-26 15:13","userId":"279216","userName":"598753468","userSign":"(如果梶浦由记能再和clamp合作一次)","message":"评分走势图不是很精细呀","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/02/09/20981.jpg","floor":"#19","id":"1384457","time":"2018-9-26 15:17","userId":"junegotist","userName":"箱神","userSign":"(May you find your worth in the waking world.)","message":"好东西<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/72.gif\" smileid=\"111\" alt=\"(bgm95)\">支持！","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/10/40/104035.jpg","floor":"#20","id":"1384459","time":"2018-9-26 15:24","userId":"lethargic_squir","userName":"瞌睡的松鼠🐿️","userSign":"(Zu jeder Zeit, an jeder Ort, bleibt das Tun, der M ...)","message":"很不错的东西<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/01.gif\" smileid=\"40\" alt=\"(bgm24)\">","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/30/91/309121.jpg","floor":"#21","id":"1384460","time":"2018-9-26 15:27","userId":"309121","userName":"娶妻不如养妹妹","userSign":"(まこと人生は......おもしろい)","message":"终于可以看游戏的分布了<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/01.gif\" smileid=\"40\" alt=\"(bgm24)\">","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/01/03/10327.jpg","floor":"#22","id":"1384465","time":"2018-9-26 16:18","userId":"jellyinside","userName":"時計坂しぐれ☘️","userSign":"(ハロ/ハワユ)","message":"班固民<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/27/37/273701.jpg","floor":"#23","id":"1384475","time":"2018-9-26 17:24","userId":"273701","userName":"AVVENIRE","user